Class CloudFormCreateStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo

          • com.carrotgarden.maven.aws.cfn.CloudFormCreateStack
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo

    public class CloudFormCreateStack
extends CloudForm
    cloud formation: create stack based on: stack name, stack template (stackTemplateFile), stack parameters (stackPropertiesInputFile + stackInputParams), and produce a stack output (stackPropertiesOutputFile) as well as inject output into into project.properties ; wait for completion or fail (CloudForm.stackTimeout);
